label interlude_4:

    play music yo_p0 fadeout 1

    show frog sensei
    with easeinright

    fs "Konnichiwa Ribbit. Do you know what anime is?"

    hide frog sensei
    with easeoutright

    show ann disgust
    with easeinleft

    a "Log on! We're at an anime convention!" with vpunch

    hide ann
    with easeoutleft

    ann_thoughts "He better not start blabbing about conventions again."

    show frog sensei
    with easeinright

    fs "Anime is nothing more then a phantasm ribbit."

    hide frog sensei
    with easeoutright

    ann_thoughts "Isn't that the point? Anime are just cartoons."

    show ann smug
    with easeinleft

    a "Wow that's really {size=8}not{/size} deep."

    hide ann
    with easeoutleft

    show frog sensei
    with easeinright

    fs "Anime isn't the only phantasm on the lillypad ribbit. The media, social networks, and even memes deceive us."

    hide frog sensei
    with easeoutright

    ann_thoughts "Wow this is pretty lame. That lies exist shouldn't come as a surprise to anyone."

    show ann smug
    with easeinleft

    a "Wow You should {size=8}{i}tee hee{/i}{/size} major in Philosophy if you haven't already."

    hide ann
    with easeoutleft

    show frog sensei
    with easeinright

    fs "Maybe one day you will understand ribbit! Sayonara tadpole!"

    hide frog sensei
    with easeoutright

    return
